Package org.apache.tika.metadata

Interface Photoshop

  • public interface Photoshop
    XMP Photoshop metadata schema. A collection of property constants for the Photo Metadata properties defined in the XMP Photoshop standard.
    Since:
    Apache Tika 1.2
